sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (React Frontend)
    participant CDN as CDN / Edge Cache
    participant R as Redis Cache
    participant CS as Category Service
    participant DB as Category DB (Postgres/Mongo)

    U->>CDN: Request categories.json
    alt Cache Hit
        CDN-->>U: Return cached categories
    else Cache Miss
        U->>CS: GET /api/categories
        CS->>R: Check Redis for categories
        alt Cache Hit
            R-->>CS: Categories found
            CS-->>U: Return categories
        else Cache Miss
            CS->>DB: Query categories
            DB-->>CS: Categories data
            CS->>R: Update Redis
            CS->>CDN: Push categories.json update
            CS-->>U: Return categories
        end
    end
